{* bound(_x) tests whether the parameter _x is not a free variable                  *}
{* The 'bound' predicate is used to check whether so-called required parameters     *}
{* of a generic query class are instantiated in a call of that query class.         *}
{* This predicate is used in generated code, i.e. in OB.rule.                       *}
{* See also ticket #147.                                                            *}

bound(_x) :- var(_x),!,fail.
bound(_x).



